						<summary>

						<p>Inscription A records that one Malaiya Nāyakkar of Maṅgalam village donated a land as <hi rend="italic">bhūdhāṉam</hi> to a <hi rend="italic">brāhmaṇa</hi> on the occasion of his marriage. Inscription B also refers the similar gift and C is much damaged.</p>						

						</summary>
